channel.description:
EDIT: clickingbuttons.java error fixed thanks to Reaper, still issue with Playerassist.java
[code]src\server\model\players\PlayerAssistant.java:315: error: cannot find symbol c.usingROD = false; ^ symbol: variable usingROD location: variable c of type Client src\server\model\players\PlayerAssistant.java:316: error: cannot find symbol c.usingGamesNeck = false; ^ symbol: variable usingGamesNeck location: variable c of type Client src\server\model\players\PlayerAssistant.java:322: error: cannot find symbol c.usingROD = false; ^ symbol: variable usingROD location: variable c of type Client src\server\model\players\PlayerAssistant.java:323: error: cannot find symbol c.usingGamesNeck = false; ^ symbol: variable usingGamesNeck location: variable c of type Client src\server\model\players\PlayerAssistant.java:329: error: cannot find symbol c.usingROD = false; ^ symbol: variable usingROD location: variable c of type Client src\server\model\players\PlayerAssistant.java:330: error: cannot find symbol c.usingGamesNeck = false; ^ symbol: variable usingGamesNeck location: variable c of type Client src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:1748: error: duplicate cas e label case 9190: ^ src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2008: error: duplicate cas e label case 9191: ^ src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2249: error: duplicate cas e label case 9192: ^ src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2460: error: duplicate cas e label case 9193: ^ src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2689: error: duplicate cas e label case 9194: ^ 11 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Im not sure what the error is, and I know i probably look like a complete Noob but...im still getting used to this. :)

item.dc:creator: @divinationofgods divinationofgods
item.description:
@divinationofgods wrote:

[quote=“ReaperXScape, post:4, topic:548134”][quote]
src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2008: error: duplicate case label
case 9191:
^
src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2249: error: duplicate case label
case 9192:
^
src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2460: error: duplicate case label
case 9193:
^
src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2689: error: duplicate case label
case 9194:
[/quote]

in that error, the compiler is telling you that you already have those same “cases” within one “switch” statement.
just take your code and move it to the other cases for those ids, or remove the other ones, and it should work.[/quote]

That fixed that, now im still not understanding the playerassist errors

item.dc:creator: @ReaperXScape ReaperXScape
item.description:
@ReaperXScape wrote:

src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2008: error: duplicate case label case 9191: ^ src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2249: error: duplicate case label case 9192: ^ src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2460: error: duplicate case label case 9193: ^ src\server\model\players\packets\ClickingButtons.java:2689: error: duplicate case label case 9194:

in that error, the compiler is telling you that you already have those same “cases” within one “switch” statement.
just take your code and move it to the other cases for those ids, or remove the other ones, and it should work.
